citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:45 pm on 25-APR-
2023. The inspector knocked on the door, honked horn, called and left voicemail, and spoke to a neighbor. Neighbor
stated the licensee had moved.
End Section
